<item>
            <title>[MCHECKSTYLE-149] supressionsFileExpression does not work.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MCHECKSTYLE-149</link>
                <project id="12317223" key="MCHECKSTYLE">Maven Checkstyle Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In DefaultCheckstyleExecutor.getOverridingProperties() there is the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; ( request.getSuppressionsFileExpression() != &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt; )
        {
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; suppresionFile = request.getSuppressionsFileExpression();

            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; ( suppresionFile != &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt; )
            {
                p.setProperty( request.getSuppressionsFileExpression(), suppresionFile );
            }
        }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note how supressionFile is being set to the &lt;b&gt;expression&lt;/b&gt;, not the &lt;b&gt;file&lt;/b&gt;.  This one line should read:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;            &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; suppresionFile = request.getSuppressionsLocation();
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This bug is blocking the m2e-checkstyle plugin from supporting Maven-driven suppression files.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
